    Runs the SWAP model

    run_swap.Rd

    Runs the SWAP model

    Usage

    run_swap(
  project_path,
  swap_file = "swap.swp",
  autoset_output = F,
  verbose = F,
  timeout = Inf,
  quiet = F
)

    Arguments

    project_path

    String, path to the project directory.

    autoset_output

    If set to true, rswap will automatically detect your observed data provided in the observed file and match it to the SWAP output. if this is set to false, then INLIST csv must be set by the user either manually or with set_swap_output() or change_swap_par()

    verbose

    logical, print status?

    timeout

    number of seconds before run timeout (optional, unlimited by default)

    quiet

    logical, turn off warnings?

    string

    name of the *.swp main file

    Value

    returns name of run (change this!)
